Output demos/vhs/out/03-swarm-dashboard.mp4
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1080
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "# Second pane: swarm_watch.py (live file from hooks)" Enter
Sleep 600ms

Hide
Type "bash demos/vhs/bin/animate-swarm.sh" Enter
Sleep 10s
Show